  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <header>
    <a href="/hydratedaily" class="logo">Hydrate<span>Daily</span></a>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>
  </header>

  <div class="intro">
    The short version: HydrateDaily stores all your data on your device only. We do not collect, transmit, or sell any personal information.
  </div>

  <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
  <p>HydrateDaily is developed and maintained by rawbuild.de. If you have any questions about this policy, you can contact us at <a href="mailto:info@rawbuild.de">info@rawbuild.de</a>.</p>

  <h2>2. Data we do NOT collect</h2>
  <p>HydrateDaily does not collect, store, transmit, or share any of the following:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Personal identification information (name, email, phone number)</li>
    <li>Account credentials (no account is required to use the app)</li>
    <li>Location data</li>
    <li>Health or fitness data uploaded to any server</li>
    <li>Analytics or behavioural tracking data</li>
    <li>Device identifiers or advertising IDs</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="highlight">
    <p>💧 All your hydration data — logs, goals, streaks, check-ins — is stored locally on your device and never leaves it.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>3. Data stored on your device</h2>
  <p>The following data is stored locally using your device's secure storage. It is never transmitted to any server:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Daily water intake logs (amount, drink type, timestamp)</li>
    <li>Your daily hydration goal</li>
    <li>Reminder preferences and waking hours</li>
    <li>Daily feel check-in responses</li>
    <li>Streak history and milestone records</li>
    <li>App settings and preferences</li>
  </ul>
  <p>You can delete all stored data at any time via Settings → Data → Reset all data. Uninstalling the app also removes all stored data.</p>

  <h2>4. Notifications</h2>
  <p>HydrateDaily uses local notifications — notifications generated on your device, not sent from a server. No data is transmitted to send you a reminder. You can disable notifications at any time in your device's Settings.</p>

  <h2>5. Third-party services</h2>
  <p>HydrateDaily does not integrate any third-party analytics tools, advertising SDKs, crash reporting services, social login providers, or external APIs. All features work entirely on-device with no external network calls.</p>

  <h2>6. Children's privacy</h2>
  <p>HydrateDaily is rated 4+ and is safe for use by children. Because we do not collect any personal data, there is no special risk to children's privacy. Parents can review and delete all app data via Settings → Data → Reset all data.</p>

  <h2>7. Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>If we make material changes to this privacy policy, we will update the "Last updated" date at the top of this page and, where appropriate, notify users via an in-app notice. Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

  <h2>8. Your rights</h2>
  <p>Because all data is stored locally on your device and we have no access to it, exercising rights such as data access, correction, or deletion is handled entirely by you — through the app's Reset feature or by uninstalling the app. If you have any questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@rawbuild.de">info@rawbuild.de</a>.</p>

  <h2>9. Contact</h2>
  <p>rawbuild.de<br>
  Email: <a href="mailto:info@rawbuild.de">info@rawbuild.de</a><br>
  Support: <a href="https://rawbuild.de/hydratedaily/support">rawbuild.de/hydratedaily/support</a></p>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2026 rawbuild.de · <a href="/hydratedaily">Hydrate Daily</a> · <a href="https://rawbuild.de/hydratedaily/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> · <a href="https://rawbuild.de/hydratedaily/support">Support</a></p>
  </footer>

</div>
</body>
